<PageLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy | TokenCalc AI" 
  description="Privacy Policy for TokenCalc AI. Learn how we handle your data and ensure your privacy."
>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: June 2026</p>

  <p>At <strong>TokenCalc AI</strong>, your privacy is our top priority. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our website.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We do not collect, store, or transmit any of the text, prompts, or sensitive information you enter into the TokenCalc AI calculator. Our tool is designed to run <strong>100% client-side</strong>, meaning all calculations and data processing occur directly within your web browser.</p>

  <p>We may collect standard, anonymized analytics data (such as browser type, pages visited, and time spent on the site) to help us improve the user experience and optimize our services.</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
  <p>The minimal, anonymized analytical data we collect is used solely for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Monitoring website performance and uptime.</li>
    <li>Understanding general user trends and improving the site's design.</li>
    <li>Identifying and fixing technical issues.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
  <p>We use standard local storage within your browser to save your theme preferences (e.g., light mode or dark mode). We do not use tracking cookies or third-party advertising cookies.</p>

  <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>Our website may contain links to third-party services (such as OpenAI, Anthropic, or Google pricing pages). We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external sites. We encourage you to read their privacy policies before providing any personal information.</p>

  <h2>5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated revision date. By continuing to use TokenCalc AI after changes are made, you agree to the revised policy.</p>

  <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please visit our <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a> page.</p>

</PageLayout>
